/green-day-trump-stupid-white-people-1822731">“未受过教育的白人工人阶级”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-trump-stupid-white-people-1822731">，</a>并将他与希特勒进行了比较。他还告诉一位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-joe-armstrong-tells-trump-supporting-fan-to-stop-listening-to-green-day-2204587" rel="noopener noreferrer">同情特朗普的粉丝不要再听绿日乐队的音乐</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3773215" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3773215" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3773215" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="绿日乐队比莉·乔·阿姆斯特朗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/green-day-live-credit-Sergione-InfusoCorbis-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3773215" class="wp-caption-text">绿日乐队的比利·乔·阿姆斯特朗 图片来源：Sergione Infuso/Corbis via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>其他表达支持副总裁的艺人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-on-eve-of-us-election-3809580">Lady Gaga</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-endorses-kamala-harris-at-houston-rally-im-here-as-a-mother-3806513">碧昂丝</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tayl